articles.title: Rory McIlroy completes magnificent season as DP World Tour number one - The42
articles.description: McIlroy tops the end-of-season European rankings with fourth-place finish in Dubai.
articles.content:
RORY MCILROY SIGNED off on a superb 2022 by finishing on top of the DP World Tour standings for the season.
